            <div class="content">
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/kkd/about-the-ministry/other-political-staff/state-secretary-lotte-grepp-knutsen.html?id=582347" title="">
                    State Secretary Lotte Grepp Knutsen
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                
                <p id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_listingUniversal_lstUniversal_ctl01_P2">
                    The Office of the Prime Minister appointed Lotte Grepp Knutsen as State Secretary in the Ministry of Culture on 20 October 2009. From January to August in 2010 she was acting State Secretary at the Office of the Prime Minister.


                </p>
                
                
