                    State Secretary Lubna Jaffery Fjell
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                
                <p id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_listingUniversal_lstUniversal_ctl02_P2">
                    Lubna Jaffery Fjell was appointed State Secretary in the Ministry of Culture on 23 October 2009. Lubna Jaffery Fjell’s previous position was that of Political Adviser to the ministers Bjarne Håkon Hanssen and Dag Terje Andersen in the Ministry of Labour and Social Inclusion.
                </p>
                
                
