            <div class="content">
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/kkd/about-the-ministry/other-political-staff/political-adviser-roger-remme-solheim.html?id=583029" title="">
                    Political Adviser Roger Remme Solheim
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                
                <p id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_listingUniversal_lstUniversal_ctl03_P2">
                    Roger Solheim was appointed Political Adviser for Minister of Culture Anniken Huitfeldt on 28 October 2009. Solheim’s previous position was that of Head of Information in the Football Association of Norway (NFF). From 13 January until 16 August 2010 he was appointed acting State Secretary in the Ministry of Culture.  
                </p>
                
                
